Directed by Saad Khan.

Written by Aditya Bharadwaj. Vamsidhar Bhogaraju. Vamsidhar Bhogaraju. Maaz Khan. Saad Khan. Saad Khan. Baadal Nanjundaswamy. Danish Sait. Darius Sunawala.

Cast Prakash Belawadi (KGB 1). Geetanjali Kulkarni (Mrs. Dalal 1). Varun Thakur (Karan Kapoor 1). Danish Sait (Nograj 1). Andrea Ravera (Vladimir 1). Sal Yusuf (Dimitri 1). Anantha Velu (Governor Govardhan 1). Vijay Chendoor (Manjunath 1). Mahantesh Hiremath (Manjay 1). Raaghu Raamanakoppa (Gurudas 1). Disha Madan (Simi Naveen 1). Mohammed Ashraf (Azam Khan 1). Pradeep (Shivvu 1). Rekha (Mrs. Kiran 1). Deepak (Dhananjay 1). Nitesh (Inspector Chikkegowda 1). Santhosh Mavinkurve (Sanjay 1). Shivakumar Aradhya (Pushpesh 1). Shobha (MLA Rani 1). Shalini Narayan (Gowri 1). Srivatsa (Ram Rehman 1). Prakash Shenoy (Mla Kiran 1). Sujatha (Indulekha 1). Sathish Chandra (Mla Shashidhar 1). Malathi (Nograj’s Mother 1)

Language Kannada.

Producers Nandishakumar D.P.. Prasoon Garg. Shoeb Hussain. Percy Karkaria. Maaz Khan. Saad Khan. Krishna. Kanchan Mahadik. Ranjib Mazumder. Vighnesh Menon. Arjun Mogre. Sameer Nair. Baladutt Papne. Akash Pothu. Danish Sait. Kartik Shah. Abhinav Pratap Singh.

Production Rainshine Entertainment. First Action Studios. Applause Entertainment Ltd..

No. of Seasons 1

No. of Episodes 10
